dcterms:creator: D. Burnner
G. Lemonie
L. Bruzzone
dcterms:description: The Sulzberger dataset is captured at Sulzberger Ice Shelf by Envisat satellite of the European Space Agency on March 11 and 16, 2011, respectively. It is used for change detection in SAR images.
dcterms:title: Sulzberger dataset

dcterms:creator: Y. Gao
F. Gao
J. Dong
S. Wang
dcterms:description: The Yellow River I dataset is captured at the Yellow River Estuary by Radarsat-2 in June 2008. It is used for change detection in SAR images and is noted for its strong speckle noise.
dcterms:title: Yellow River I dataset

dcterms:creator: Y. Gao
F. Gao
J. Dong
S. Wang
dcterms:description: The Yellow River II dataset is captured at the Yellow River Estuary by Radarsat-2 in June 2009. It is used for change detection in SAR images and is also affected by strong speckle noise.
dcterms:title: Yellow River II dataset
